fullTextAnnotation.text:
Keyboards
Computers
EN: College Compressed Gas. For the high
pressure cleaning of electronic equipments,
inner parts of PCs, TVs, faxes, copying
machines, printers, phones, etc. Easily and very
effectively removes dirt and dust also from the
most hidden parts. Leaves no residue. Keep the
can in upright position. Date of production: on
the bottom of can.
EE: College Surugaas. Krge survega saab
elektroonilisi seadmeid, arvutikorpuse sisemust, televiisoreid,
printereid, telefone. Kergesti ja efektiivselt eemaldab mustust ja
skesti ligipsetavatest kohtadest. Ei jta jke. Hoida purki pstises
miskuupev asub purgi all.
saspiestais gaiss. Tiroais ldzeklis ar augstu spiedienu, kas ir
storu, TV, faksu, kopjamo manu, printeru, telefonu un citu
